  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "BIM Modeler",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Create, develop and model detailing</p></li><li><p>Develop and update BIM models using software like Autodesk Revit, Navisworks, or similar tools.</p></li><li><p>Ensure models align with project specifications and standards.</p></li><li><p>Prepare for authorities submissions documentation and construction documentation.</p></li><li><p>Create realistic, intelligent and highly accurate BIM models of Building Exteriors and Building Interiors</p></li><li><p>Include precise and valuable pre-construction information such as Material Specifications, Quantities Estimates, Time Schedules, Costs Estimates</p></li><li><p>Create libraries/ Families of information related to Standards, various styles, building components specifications necessary for engineering co-ordination.</p></li><li><p>Provide technical support to team members in resolving modeling issues.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Diploma/Degree in Structural/Architecture/Engineering/Construction/MEP or equivalent.</p></li><li><p>Minimally 2 years’ experience in building construction and project execution.</p></li><li><p>Knowledge and experience in Revit, AutoCAD, Navisworks.</p></li></ul><p><strong>HOW TO APPLY:</strong></p><p>Interested applicants, kindly send your resume in MS WORD format or please click on “Apply Now”.</p><p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>Important Note: Trust Recruit Pte Ltd is committed to safeguarding your personal data in accordance with the Personal Data Protection Act (PDPA).</p><p>Please read our privacy statement on our corporate website.</p><p>Trust Recruit Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No: 19C9950</p><p>EA Personnel: Tan Sin Yong (Stella)</p><p>EA Personnel Reg No: R24124127</p>",
